-- McQuilling and Atlas Form New Venture for Ship-Financing
-- B y   A l a r i c   N i g h t i n g a l e
-- 2012-11-29T07:48:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-29/mcquilling-and-atlas-form-new-venture-for-ship-financing.html
McQuilling Partners Inc., a New
York-based shipbroker and consultant, formed a venture with
Atlas Holdings Hong Kong Ltd. to arrange financing for shipping
transactions.  McQuilling Atlas Advisors will organize funding from
private equity, lenders, and alternative finance providers,
McQuilling said in an e-mailed statement yesterday. It will also
give financial advice during mergers and acquisitions.  To contact the reporter on this story:
